The humans have long indulged themselves in consumption and they overlooked the fact that the ecosystem of the
earth was made mostly of bacteria, viruses, and plants. Plants are vital for existence as they provide oxygen for the atmoshpere. Even if the humans should become extinct, it will not endanger the ecosystem. However, it does imperil the humans if the plants, bacteria and viruses become extinct. Carrier's theme is to call attention to the humans, the arrogant apes who believe they reign supreme over all life on the planet. They are in fact at the mercy
of the ecosystem. Unlock the mystery of the giant aircraft carrier and its cargo. Your job as a member of a hand-picked squad is to board the Heimdall and determine what has happened to the ship, crew, and the mysterious life form.